graph TD
  Start((Start)) --> Msg1[Send Greeting]
  Msg1 --> WaitBuy[Wait for Signal: Buy]
  WaitBuy --> Msg2[Send Success]
  Msg2 --> Msg3[Notify Manager]
  Msg3 --> WaitMan[Wait for Signal: Manager Action]
  WaitMan --> Decision{Action?}
  Decision -- Accept --> Delivery[Delivery Saga]
  Decision -- Close --> EndB((End: Cancelled))
  Decision -- Ask --> Msg4[Ask Client: Delay]
  Msg4 --> WaitClient[Wait for Signal: Client Response]
  WaitClient -- Cancel --> EndC((End: Cancelled))
  WaitClient -- Wait --> Delivery
  Delivery --> EndA((End: Completed))